{"tid":1780601,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"JJ插沙 送花送一枝會唔會唔係咁好？","createTime":"2019-12-12T13:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T08:12:34.000Z","uid":194894,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6822093e5fda0567693b786d5f43a9aab58edbd6","tid":1780601,"uid":194894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:18:54.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n背景：同女朋友拍左接近四年拖，最近激嬲左佢，話我懶左（對呢個關係），無以前拍拖個陣咁sweet，呢點我又認。<br />\n<br />\n所以黎緊我諗住每個月都送一次花比佢，等佢開心下又好，當提醒下自己唔好懶都好。<br />\n<br />\n但係我仲係學生，如果個個月都一束束咁送 我諗我未必負擔到。我想好似啲鬼佬咁無端白事送花個種感覺，所以大家覺得送幾多枝好？"},{"pid":"1bec167c71d661aa2f18f9ddfa5527cb66141f90","tid":1780601,"uid":75597,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:20:31.000Z","msg":"睇錯好似白事送花咁既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n送太多次唔好啦<br />\n一次送紮細細地接佢放工/放學咪算"},{"pid":"0817259c2cd5a8886234d35e46fb9a8ba9a3c93e","tid":1780601,"uid":19645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:20:59.000Z","msg":"送花都沒心思啦，種俾佢吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4ceb346bd4aac747a94f612c56369e31444f39","tid":1780601,"uid":194894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bec167c71d661aa2f18f9ddfa5527cb66141f90","tid":1780601,"uid":75597,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:20:31.000Z","msg":"睇錯好似白事送花咁既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n送太多次唔好啦<br />\n一次送紮細細地接佢放工/放學咪算"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:22:22.000Z","msg":"細細地一紮大約幾枝好？因為我真係無送過鮮花比佢，無咩概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3e13118b7343791ad982ace0ed909dcf7237f7","tid":1780601,"uid":145987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:24:24.000Z","msg":"多少唔重要 最緊要佢知你有心"},{"pid":"4bebbc03cf2bd0b7ed7a1a7c24a2ba5d3e80406f","tid":1780601,"uid":194894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0817259c2cd5a8886234d35e46fb9a8ba9a3c93e","tid":1780601,"uid":19645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:20:59.000Z","msg":"送花都沒心思啦，種俾佢吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:24:30.000Z","msg":"試過種 屋企唔啱位種極都唔靚或者死 可能我手勢唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22824e2aa7070d3ee9b0459babb45e1a3e6961c9","tid":1780601,"uid":194894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be3e13118b7343791ad982ace0ed909dcf7237f7","tid":1780601,"uid":145987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:24:24.000Z","msg":"多少唔重要 最緊要佢知你有心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:25:37.000Z","msg":"我都係咁諗，但係啱先睇完高登9年前有個post又係送一枝 個樓主被分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a3fce74ae5fff82909e27d63d3b604dbf959f9","tid":1780601,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:31:19.000Z","msg":"自己摺<br />\n加個容器(要靚)<br />\n然後話每個月送一朵，個容器放滿花就點點點(睇佢想要咩啦)"},{"pid":"d31eb12751713dcc61ba5945b3152b24eae256c7","tid":1780601,"uid":194894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1a3fce74ae5fff82909e27d63d3b604dbf959f9","tid":1780601,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:31:19.000Z","msg":"自己摺<br />\n加個容器(要靚)<br />\n然後話每個月送一朵，個容器放滿花就點點點(睇佢想要咩啦)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime